.TH "GLOBAL C_ASCII_DEC" 3 "" "" ""
.SH "NAME"
boost::log::expressions::c_ascii_decor
.SH "SYNOPSIS"

.sp
.nf
// In header: <boost/log/expressions/formatters/c_decorator\&.hpp>

\fIunspecified\fR c_ascii_decor;
.fi
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
C\-style decorator generator object\&. Acts similarly to
c_decor, except that
c_ascii_decor
also converts all non\-ASCII and non\-printable ASCII characters, except for space character, into C\-style hexadecimal escape sequences\&. The generator provides
operator[]
that can be used to construct the actual decorator\&. For example:
.PP
c_ascii_decor[ stream << attr< std::string >("MyAttr") ]
.PP
For wide\-character formatting there is the similar
wc_ascii_decor
decorator generator object\&.

